stories.title: Dhaniram heroics in vain as Bermuda claim series
stories.subTitle: Canada v Bermuda, 2nd ODI, King City
stories.summary: Bermuda claimed a tense 11-run victory against Canada despite Sunil Dhaniram's all-round brilliance and won the three-ODI series 2-0 in King City
